metadata.name: Lucky cat kitty
metadata.description:
lucky cat in wonderland with his dear friends They travel and adventure through time into a slot game that is a fun, colorful dimension, full of fun fortune-telling. This time they had more fun and unexpectedly found more luck. It's because they have a lucky cat. always by your side His best friend regarded him as a lucky cat for them. This story was inspired by Maneki Neko, or Maneki Neko, a talisman that Japanese people believe will attract good luck into their lives. And the legend of the maneki neko or maneki neko occurred in the Edo period around the 17th century onwards, and nowadays, the maneki neko has become a symbol of good luck and bringing wealth and success. People tend to stick it at home or trade doing various business. for good luck and wealth to come to the family.
